---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
	<section class="about">
		<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495216875107-c6c043eb703f" alt="Photographer profile" class="profile-image" />
		<div class="content">
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<p>Hello! I'm a passionate photographer dedicated to capturing the beauty of our world through my lens. With over a decade of experience, I specialize in landscape, urban, and wildlife photography.</p>
			<p>My journey in photography began when I first picked up a camera during a trip to the mountains. Since then, I've traveled across continents, capturing moments that tell stories and evoke emotions.</p>
			<h2>Equipment</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Canon EOS R5</li>
				<li>RF 24-70mm f/2.8L IS USM</li>
				<li>RF 70-200mm f/2.8L IS USM</li>
				<li>RF 15-35mm f/2.8L IS USM</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.profile-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 400px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.content {
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	h2 {
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
	}
	ul {
		list-style-type: none;
		padding: 0;
	}
	li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
	}
	li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}
</style>